" change textwidth
nnoremap <Leader>tw :set textwidth=

" change tab settings
nnoremap <Leader>2:set shiftwidth=2<CR>:set softtabstop=2<CR>:set tabstop=2<CR>
nnoremap <Leader>4:set shiftwidth=4<CR>:set softtabstop=4<CR>:set tabstop=4<CR>
